| Auth | Custom User (email-based) |
| Apps | users, catalogs, patients, professionals, appointments, payments, audits |

## Database Schema (21 tables)

- **users**: `users_user`
- **catalogs**: `catalogs_specialty`
- **patients**: `patients_profile`
